title: Enormous 1-bedroom!
posting_body: ['Luxury Apartment Living in Brentwood!', '555 Barrington is a luxury, Mediterranean-style apartment community which provides residents with all the conveniences of home in the heart of Brentwood.', 'Offering spacious one, two and three bedroom floor plans designed for comfortable living, all suites feature luxury wood-plank flooring, private balconies, nine-foot ceilings, gourmet kitchens, Italian ceramic tile entries, full size washer and dryers and fireplaces.', 'Living at 555 Barrington, you can relax and unwind in the heated pool and spa set in a lush, tropical courtyard as well work out in the fully equipped fitness center with strength training and cardio equipment.', 'For pet lovers, our community is extremely pet friendly and is located within two blocks of', 'the Veterans Barrington Dog Park for off-leash fun.', 'Best of all is the prime location where a quick stroll in either direction takes you to the trendy shops and cafes on San Vicente or to charming Brentwood Village.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 1030 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- -
